Make convenient parameters

Source: R/make_parameters.R
make_parameters_sir.Rd

Function to make convenient parameters.

Usage

make_parameters_sir(option = c("stochastic", "deterministic"))

Arguments

option

Either "stochastic" or "deterministic".

Examples

make_parameters_sir(option = "stochastic")
#> $beta
#> [1] 0.1
#> 
#> $gamma
#> [1] 0.05
#> 
#> $N
#> [1] 1000
#> 
#> $S0
#> [1] 999
#> 
#> $I0
#> [1] 1
#> 
#> $R0
#> [1] 0
#> 
#> $tf
#> [1] 200
#>
